OL,3,COverhaul for minibus due to passengers
OL,4,C'abusing the service'
OL,6,FMajor changes to the Westlink minibus
OL,7,Fservice are planned in April.
OL,9,FThe dial-a-ride minibuses operate
OL,10,Facross the Bristol region but
OL,11,Faccording to the West of England
OL,12,FCombined Authority, some users are
OL,13,Fbooking trips far longer than intended
OL,14,Fcausing the service serious issues.
OL,16,FWestlink was launched in April last
OL,17,Fyear, and is known as "demand
OL,18,Fresponsive transport".
OL,26,@yD@WOUzD@UO]
