OL,3,COverhaul for minibus due to passengers
OL,4,C'abusing the service'
OL,6,FPassengers book a trip on an app, and
OL,7,Fa bright green minibus picks them up
OL,8,Fand takes them to existing bus routes
OL,9,Ffor a #2 fare.
OL,11,FThe service, set up by the West of
OL,12,FEngland Combined Authority, has faced
OL,13,Fseveral problems including a shortage
OL,14,Fof drivers.
OL,16,FFrom this April, the bus' transport
OL,17,Fzones will be made much smaller, to
OL,18,Fstop passengers from booking
OL,19,Fexcessively long trips, such as to
OL,20,FBristol Airport.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/14
