OL,3,COverhaul for minibus due to passengers
OL,4,C'abusing the service'
OL,6,FBob Scowen, interim head of integrated
OL,7,Ftransport operations at the combined
OL,8,Fauthority, said: "There are changes to
OL,9,Fzones, and there also changes to what
OL,10,Fyou can do.
OL,12,F"If an alternative bus service exists
OL,13,Falready, then you have to take that
OL,14,Frather than take the whole journey
OL,15,Ffrom A to B on the minibus. There's
OL,16,Falso some improvements to through-
OL,17,Fticketing arrangements."
