OL,6,FHe was speaking to councillors on the
OL,7,FWest of England audit committee,
OL,8,Fduring a public meeting on Monday 4
OL,9,FMarch.
OL,11,FThrough-ticketing means passengers
OL,12,Fwill be able to book just one ticket
OL,13,Ffor a journey involving more than one
OL,14,Fbus ride, instead of paying for each
OL,15,Fride.
OL,17,FThe scheme was "launched at the worst
OL,18,Fpossible time", according to Mr
OL,19,FScowen, due to a lack of bus drivers
OL,20,Facross the country.
OL,26,@yD@POUzD@NO]
