OL,4,C'abusing the service'
OL,6,FAt the same time, almost half the
OL,7,Fsubsidised bus routes in the West of
OL,8,FEngland were withdrawn.
OL,10,FThese routes were unprofitable but
OL,11,Freceived public funding, until local
OL,12,Fcouncils decided they could no longer
OL,13,Fafford to support them.
OL,15,FMr Scowen added: "It wasn't a direct
OL,16,Flike-for-like replacement and there
OL,17,Fhas been confusion, quite
OL,18,Funderstandably given its timing, about
OL,19,Fwhat Westlink was designed to do.
OL,26,@wD@ROU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/14
