OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F431A1709740454
OL,3,COverhaul for minibus due to passengers
OL,4,C'abusing the service'
OL,6,F"It was never designed to and never
OL,7,Fcan replace the withdrawn fixed
OL,8,Fservices in rural areas.
OL,10,F"It was designed entirely differently,
OL,11,Ffor a different purpose. That's to
OL,12,Fcomplement the existing network, which
OL,13,Fmany rural areas had no connection
OL,14,Fwhatsoever to. It's been unfairly
OL,15,Fblamed in many ways, for something it
OL,16,Fcould never deliver in the first place.
OL,26,@rD@AOU
