OL,3,COverhaul for minibus due to passengers
OL,4,C'abusing the service'
OL,6,F"We launched it at the very worst
OL,7,Fpossible time, it was quite ambitious
OL,8,Fto launch it in three months. The
OL,9,Ftruth is there was a national shortage
OL,10,Fof bus drivers, which is still
OL,11,Factually an issue.
OL,13,F"To try and launch it when First Bus,
OL,14,Fthe principal operator in the region,
OL,15,Fhad 250 agency drivers was obviously
OL,16,Fquite challenging. It's now vastly
OL,17,Fmore reliable than it was when we
OL,18,Flaunched it.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
