OL,3,COverhaul for minibus due to passengers
OL,4,C'abusing the service'
OL,6,F"While the combined authority has
OL,7,Fdenied Westlink replaced the cut bus
OL,8,Fservices, the scheme was introduced at
OL,9,Fthe same time the services were
OL,10,Fwithdrawn.
OL,12,F"Westlink faced teething problems from
OL,13,Fits outset, with some passengers
OL,14,Fstruggling to book trips and a
OL,15,Fshortage of drivers.
OL,17,F"Transport bosses were only granted an
OL,18,Foperator licence days before the
OL,19,Fscheme launched."
OL,26,@nD@AO]
