OL,4,C'abusing the service'
OL,6,FThe West of England did not run a full
OL,7,Fmarketing campaign to promote the
OL,8,Fscheme, due to concerns that the
OL,9,Fshortage of drivers meant the service
OL,10,Fwould not be able to meet the
OL,11,Fincreased demand that a campaign would
OL,12,Fgenerate.
OL,14,FAround seven per cent of journeys
OL,15,Ftaken so far have been over 10 miles
OL,16,Flong, but "very long journeys should
OL,17,Fnot have been possible".
OL,26,@xD@KOUyD@WO]
