OL,4,C'abusing the service'
OL,6,FLabour Councillor Tim Rippington,
OL,7,Frepresenting Brislington East, said:
OL,8,F"The impression I get was that DRT
OL,9,Fwasn't really ready at that point and
OL,10,Fit was rushed in.
OL,12,F"You didn't really have enough
OL,13,Fdrivers, the vehicles had to be
OL,14,Fprepared very quickly, and part of the
OL,15,Ffallout from that was the service
OL,16,Fdidn't really work in a way that it
OL,17,Fwas supposed to.
OL,26,@pD@AOU
