OL,4,C'abusing the service'
OL,6,F"A lot of people couldn't get the
OL,7,Fjourneys they wanted, and so you kind
OL,8,Fof had a loss of confidence early on
OL,9,Fin the service."
OL,11,FLiberal Democrat Cllr Toby Simon,
OL,12,Frepresenting Bathwick, added: "My
OL,13,Funderstanding is that there were a
OL,14,Fnumber of users who were effectively
OL,15,Fabusing the service. Somebody was
OL,16,Fcommuting from Keynsham to Clevedon.
