OL,4,C'abusing the service'
OL,6,F"Another issue is that Westlink will
OL,7,Frun out of government funding in two
OL,8,Fyears. The scheme is funded from the
OL,9,FBus Service Improvement Plan, which
OL,10,Fexpires in March 2026.
OL,12,F"After that, the combined authority
OL,13,Fwill have to make the service pay for
OL,14,Fitself, but there are "potentially
OL,15,Fpretty huge" risks that it could be
OL,16,Fscrapped after the government cash
OL,17,Fdries up.
OL,26,@nD@AO]vD@WOUwD@LO]
