OL,6,FConservative Cllr Geoff Gollop, chair
OL,7,Fof the audit committee, said: "One of
OL,8,Fmy concerns is that this is coming
OL,9,Ffrom funding that runs out.
OL,11,F"What's envisaged to replace this? It
OL,12,Fseems to me that the risks of service
OL,13,Fdelivery to our residents are
OL,14,Fpotentially pretty huge.
OL,16,F"Continuing a scheme that only solves
OL,17,Fthe problem while the scheme is in
OL,18,Fplace raises a large number of
OL,19,Fquestions."
